## 9. Baseline Requirements

All baselines score the **same** candidate pools.

**Readout-side (probe ladder):** energy/onset; CLAP; SyncNet/AV-sync; ImageBind; audio tagger; MLLM-on-preview; (Phase 7) internal-feature probe.

**Policy-side (Phase 4):** full BoN; same-compute BoN; random pruning; scalar DiffRS-style rejection; final-score reranking; seed restart; **oracle axis-gated pruning (upper bound)**.

**Rollback-side (Phase 6):** Restart without axis gating; scalar rejection + rollback; full seed restart.

